rows.label: tlk70000005_01_msg0001
rows.name: I'm so glad that Joey's perked up now.

rows.label: tlk70000005_01_msg0002
rows.name:
There he was, just stewing and
worrying about his Armus. Why didn't
he just come and ask me for help?

rows.label: tlk70000005_01_msg0003
rows.name:
That's what I told him. But he just said,
"You're not a grown-up yet. Chill out!"

rows.label: tlk70000005_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Yeah, he said that, but so what? I've
some responsibility here. Like my job
attracting customers to the inn.

rows.label: tlk70000005_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I've gotta think about what the guests
like, how our brand is perceived...
Tons of stuff!

rows.label: tlk70000005_01_msg0006
rows.name:
And worrying about Joey
is a full-time job in itself!
